extends layout
block content
    section.jumbotron.center-text.transparent
      h1 MangaDB
      h2 Track your personal manga collection.
      if !user
        button#btn-hide.btn.btn-success(type='button', onclick="window.location.href='/signup'") Create account
    main.main.opacity
      section.container-fluid.center-text
        .row
          .col-sm-4.col-lg-4
            i.fa.fa-bolt.fa-5x
            h3 Quick Access
            p
              | Because you can never keep track of which manga you have read or are reading online, this site will help you keep track and have quick access to the manga you add to your collection. No more forgetting or having to keep bookmarks!
          .col-sm-4.col-lg-4
            i.fa.fa-globe.fa-5x
            h3 Site Agnostic
            p
              | While no manga is hosted here, you can read the physical copy or read the manga online. You are able to keep links to a manga series from any popular sites, which means you can have manga from different sites kept here in your personal collection.
          .col-sm-4.col-lg-4
            i.fa.fa-lock.fa-5x
            h3 Secured Account
            p
              | Because you might not want others to see what you like to read, having your own account means not only access to the service but protection of your information from attackers and other users. Read worry free!
      section#push
